ave succeeded.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3848 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33279,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/21\/no-dua-is-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":20043,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: No request better than for wellness in world, Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo supplication a servant can say is better than this: O Allah, I ask You for wellness in the world and in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3851 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/09\/iman-husn-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":20043,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Ask Allah for faith with good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for the health of my faith, such faith with good character, and salvation followed by success, Your mercy, Your wellness, Your forgiveness, and Your pleasure.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8255 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/ask-for-good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20043,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Why not ask for good in this life and the Hereafter?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, visited a sick man among the Muslims and he was so emaciated that he was like thin bird. The Prophet said to him, \u201cHave you supplicated for anything or asked from Allah?\u201d The man said, \u201cYes. I said:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/dua-new-convert-revert\/","url_meta":{"origin":20043,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for a new convert to Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Tariq ibn al-Ashyam reported: Whenever a man embraced Islam, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would teach him the prayer. Then, the Prophet instructed him to supplicate with these words, \u201cO Allah, forgive me, have mercy on me, guide me, grant me wellness, and provide for me.\" The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/categor